  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Effect Mechanism Investigation of a Wearable Electrostimulator for Rapid Alleviation of
      Parkinson's Disease Symptoms
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Activation levels of interested regions of the brain will be measured through fMRI technique
      prior and after the dry needling and active stimulation applications.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
